## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run build` using the terminal to assure Vite builds the project without syntax errors.

### Manual Verification
- Start the dev server (`npm run dev`).
- Open the application in the browser.
- Navigate to the "aSS Originals" category.
- Verify `cyberpipes` and `voxelcity` are available in the list.
- Click on each new effect and the updated `matrix` effect.
- Ensure they render beautifully without WebGL errors and run at a smooth framerate.
